    journal = "Talenta Conference Series: Science and Technology (ST)",
    booktitle = "Talenta Conference Series: Science and Technology (ST)",
    abstract = "Dictionary is a reference that contains words and phrases that are usually sorted alphabetically and is followed by a description of the word or phrase. Dictionary consists of several types, one of which is a dictionary of terms. Psychology dictionary is a dictionary of terms that contain psychological term. Psychology dictionary is identical to the old tome in search and less efficient in its use. Made an Android-based application of psychology dictionary that applies the Horspool algorithm for terms search and SQLite for data storage is a solution. The search algorithm is needed to shorten the time in the search itself. Horspool algorithm apply a saved search information to shift even further because the string matching is done from right to left, so the time to search a string is shorter. Fields used in this research is psychology in general terms. By entering a psychological term as input in the search then we will get the search results. The results of this research show the entire pattern that matches the text.",
